WEBVTT

00:01:27.157 --> 00:01:31.232
ilikuwa ya 177 kwa ubora wa maisha duniani.

00:01:31.256 --> 00:01:32.460
hali Ilikuwa mbaya.

00:01:34.270 --> 00:01:38.729
Sasa, afya ya uchumi inategemea afya ya mashirika ambayo huifanya.

00:01:39.187 --> 00:01:40.337
Hivyo serikali -

00:01:40.361 --> 00:01:42.106
moja ya taasisi zake muhimu -

00:01:42.130 --> 00:01:43.568
inapokuwa dhaifu au ina afya mbaya,

00:01:43.592 --> 00:01:45.575
kila mtu na kila kitu vinateseka.

00:01:46.522 --> 00:01:49.295
Wakati mwingine unaweza kuweka plasta

00:01:49.319 --> 00:01:51.831
kujaribu kupunguza maumivu kwa muda

00:01:52.732 --> 00:01:54.714
Labda baadhi yenu hapa mmeshiriki

00:01:54.738 --> 00:01:57.717
katika wimbi la utoaji misaada Afrika --

00:01:57.741 --> 00:02:02.223
kuanzisha shule mbadala,
kujenga hospitali, kuchimba visima --